{"tid":623673,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"韓版《毒戰》公開新海報","createTime":"2018-04-10T08:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T08:04:13.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"19ad702b906534a6fb3bbc1f1149acc511e53ba4","tid":623673,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"韓劇《布拉格戀人》男星金柱赫去年10月車禍身亡，令圈中好友及粉絲大感不捨。而金柱赫的遺作、韓版《毒戰》，將於下月24日上映，電影公司方面今日公開新海報，公開一眾主演金柱赫、趙震雄、柳俊烈等人的造型。<br />\n<br />\n片中，趙震雄飾演熱血刑警，柳俊烈飾演被販毒組織拋棄的聯絡人，金柱赫就飾演中國毒品組織的頭目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180410/large/1523336874_a711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180410%2Flarge%2F1523336874_a711.jpg&h=728a29e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/160400_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F160400_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7811f52a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}